Class OceanSquare

java.lang.Object
  OceanSquare

public class OceanSquare
extends java.lang.Object

Ocean square objects make up the ocean. They are used to store actors, rocks and have a plankton level.

Author:
Matthew Maglennon

regeneratePlankton

public void regeneratePlankton()
Regenerates plankton by 0.1, to be called each step. Will not exceed a plankton level of 10.
